<xsl:stylesheet xmlns:xsl="http://www.w3.org/1999/XSL/Transform" xmlns:dita="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" version="2.0" exclude-result-prefixes="dita">

	<dita:topic xmlns="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="Rosetta_remotelink-Chof-lilabel-LxAdv-Suppress">
    <title><sourcexml>lilabel/remotelink</sourcexml> to <targetxml>note</targetxml> <lnpid>id-CCCC-10462</lnpid></title>
    <body>
        <section>
            <p>If <sourcexml>remotelink</sourcexml> encounter in <sourcexml>lilabel</sourcexml>, then <sourcexml>remotelink</sourcexml> will be suppressed but its content will be retained in NL conversion.</p>
        </section>
        <example>
            <title>Source XML </title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;li&gt;
 &lt;lilabel&gt;
  &lt;remotelink dpsi="0K9G" refpt="PARA-WLPH-7-12-8" remotekey1="REFPTID" service="DOC-ID"&gt;12.8&lt;/remotelink&gt;
 &lt;/lilabel&gt;
 &lt;p&gt;
  &lt;text&gt;Agent for Service of Process&lt;/text&gt;
 &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
            </codeblock>
            <title>Target XML</title>
            <codeblock>

&lt;listitem&gt;
 &lt;label&gt;12.8&lt;/label&gt;
 &lt;bodytext&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;
   &lt;text&gt;Agent for Service of Process&lt;/text&gt;
  &lt;/p&gt;
 &lt;/bodytext&gt;
&lt;/listitem&gt;
            </codeblock>
        </example>
        <section>
            <title>Changes</title>
            <p>2012-09-27: Created.</p>
        </section>
    </body>
